passes.benefit_text:
Single coupon provides FREE admission for up to four visitors.
Does not provide access to Harvard Art Museums.
This is a non-returnable coupon pass that must be picked up at the Main Library Circulation Desk after it is reserved.&nbsp;

Half-price admission for up to 6 individuals.&nbsp;
Cannot be combined with a group tour plan. Not valid for special events.&nbsp;
This is a coupon code that will be emailed to you to use ordering tickets online. Follow the instructions in the email to recieve your discount.

Pass admits 2 people at $10.00 per person.
Valid only for the date listed on this pass.&nbsp;
This is a coupon pass that will be emailed and can be printed or displayed on your mobile screen.

Each promo code provides up to two adults with $15 admission per person and four youths (ages 7–17) with $10 admission per person.&nbsp;
Tickets to the MFA are always free for visitors under seven years old.
Valid only for the date listed on this pass.&nbsp;
This is a coupon pass that will be emailed and can be printed or displayed on your mobile screen.

Fall-Spring (Septemper 2, 2025 through May 22, 2026): &nbsp;
Pass admits up to 4 people at 50% off the cost of admission.
Summer (May 26, 2026 through September 4, 2026, weekdays only):&nbsp;
Pass&nbsp;admits up to four people (adult, senior, child, or college) at a cost of $20 each. Children under age 3 are not included in the admission count and are always admitted free.
This is a coupon pass that will be emailed and can be printed or displayed on your mobile screen.

Pass admits up to 2 people at $12 each.
Valid only for the date listed on this pass.&nbsp;
Reservations must be made in advance by visiting the Peabody Essex Museum website and using the promo code shown below the barcode on your pass.&nbsp;
This is a coupon code that will be emailed to you to use ordering tickets online. Follow the instructions in the email to recieve your discount.
